Added a few small replace values for erroneous incoming text, e.g. tonight, tomorrow, etc.
Adding small edit for Month slot capture, to change mae to May if it comes in
Last edits, removing some unnecessary cards returned to users, new Alexa certification submission
Tweaks to remove formatting to display cards, to pass certification tests

Major rewrite of AWS Music Man skill. This version structually mirrors the AWS SDK Skill Airfacts, splitting handlers into seperate classes. The latest client builders for DynamoDB and SNS replace deprecated versions in older version of this skill. The Amazon.Literal is now removed in favor of custom slots. The new skill is now using the Render Display template to improve readability and presentation on display devices like the Echo Show.
